description: This NuGet package includes the required files to create an ASP.NET MVC web application with support for the HTML5 based rich text editor of TX Text Control .NET Server for ASP.NET. Give your users an MS Word compatible document editor to create powerful reporting templates anywhere - in any HTML5-based browser including Google Chrome, Firefox, Safari and Internet Explorer. The trial version of TX Text Control .NET Server for ASP.NET is required to use this NuGet package.
summary: The HTML5 based rich text editor of TX Text Control .NET Server for ASP.NET MVC.
title: TXTextControl.Web
